--*- mode: Org; -*--

My Emacs Config files

* Setup Instructions:

** To set it up on your computer, just symlink the .emacs.d/, .emacs, etc. files to your home folder.

** Or if you don't want all that hassle, just copy it to your home folder.

** In the .emacs file:

   Replace occurrences of

   - the word "pradeep" with your username on your home computer, and 

   - the word "spradeep" with your DCF login (if you're an IITian, else this doesn't apply).
